<p><a name="Global" id="Global"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Government_debt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Global">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Global</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://blog-pfm.imf.org/" class="external text" title="http://blog-pfm.imf.org/" rel="nofollow">The IMF Public Financial Management Blog</a></li>
<li><a href="http://samvak.tripod.com/brief-sovereigndebt01.html" class="external text" title="http://samvak.tripod.com/brief-sovereigndebt01.html" rel="nofollow">Default on sovereign debt and sovereign bankruptcy</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ndir.com/SI/education/debt.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.ndir.com/SI/education/debt.shtml" rel="nofollow">Canadian debt clock (private estimate)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cluaran.free.fr/dette.html" class="external text" title="http://cluaran.free.fr/dette.html" rel="nofollow">French public debt clock</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.steuerzahler.de" class="external text" title="http://www.steuerzahler.de" rel="nofollow">Germany's debt clock (at the top of the page)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mof.go.jp/english/files.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.mof.go.jp/english/files.htm" rel="nofollow">Japan's national debt</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.takarabe-hrj.co.jp/clock/" class="external text" title="http://www.takarabe-hrj.co.jp/clock/" rel="nofollow">Japanese Debt Clock (In Ten Thousand Yen Units)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.rgk.se/" class="external text" title="http://www.rgk.se/" rel="nofollow">Riksgäldskontoret - the national debts of Sweden</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cluaran.free.fr/debt.html" class="external text" title="http://cluaran.free.fr/debt.html" rel="nofollow">UK public debt clock</a></li>
<li><a href="http://blog-pfm.imf.org/pfmblog/2007/11/7th-imf-debt-ma.html" class="external text" title="http://blog-pfm.imf.org/pfmblog/2007/11/7th-imf-debt-ma.html" rel="nofollow">7th IMF Debt Management Forum, Brian Olden, IMF/FAD</a></li>
<li><a href="http://stats.oecd.org/wbos/Index.aspx?DataSetCode=GOV_DEBT" class="external text" title="http://stats.oecd.org/wbos/Index.aspx?DataSetCode=GOV_DEBT" rel="nofollow">OECD government debt statistics</a></li>
</ul>
